# Study Buddy: Group Study Organizer

**Author:** Mandeep (200599770)
**Course:** 25F Mobile and Pervasive Computing â€“ 201
**Instructor:** Sandhya
**Date:** October 29, 2025

## Purpose
Study Buddy helps students create, join, and manage group study sessions.
It improves collaboration, communication, and organization among classmates.

## Planned Technologies
- Android Studio (Kotlin)
- Firebase Firestore (NoSQL Database)
- Firebase Authentication
- Material Design Components

## Planned Features
- Login & Signup
- Create and Join Study Groups
- Chat Messaging
- Reminders for Study Sessions
- Notifications
- Profile & Settings
